WEBVTT

01:31.380 --> 01:34.900
=Generation to Generation=

01:35.020 --> 01:37.900
=Episode 23=

01:51.130 --> 01:52.380
I've never understood

01:54.100 --> 01:56.260
why the Man in Black

01:57.180 --> 01:58.740
set ambushes everywhere and

01:59.160 --> 02:00.490
chased us all the way
since Chang Fort.

02:01.690 --> 02:02.900
Just now, I got it.

02:03.720 --> 02:04.690
Nie Zhe and the Man in Black

02:04.690 --> 02:06.540
are both so obsessed with
the Jade Sunflower.

02:07.020 --> 02:08.850
You lured me into going to Chang Fort,

02:09.220 --> 02:11.660
then tricked me into
seeking the Shi brothers.

02:12.130 --> 02:13.850
Also for the Jade Sunflower.

02:15.410 --> 02:16.500
And Lu Chengnan

02:16.880 --> 02:17.820
betrayed his master and sect

02:18.340 --> 02:19.890
just to take it.

02:21.220 --> 02:23.410
Guess the Jade Sunflower, like saliva,

02:24.010 --> 02:26.290
is an important medium
for cultivating the Ziwei Method.

02:29.660 --> 02:31.220
I knew I couldn't hide it from you.

02:34.410 --> 02:36.410
I once suspected
your sudden surge in power

02:36.410 --> 02:38.170
came from cultivating the Ziwei Method.

02:39.130 --> 02:40.610
But on the way back
from the Snow Mountain,

02:40.980 --> 02:42.010
I have already checked that

02:42.780 --> 02:44.010
the saliva hasn't decreased.

02:44.410 --> 02:45.980
If you've been
cultivating the Ziwei Method,

02:46.260 --> 02:47.940
then where did your saliva come from?

02:48.500 --> 02:49.690
When did you tamper with it?

02:50.170 --> 02:51.290
What else are you hiding from me?

02:51.290 --> 02:52.170
Zhao.

02:52.940 --> 02:54.820
I got the saliva purely by accident.

03:04.660 --> 03:05.780
It actually worked.

03:06.980 --> 03:08.610
This wasn't my intention.

03:11.940 --> 03:13.690
You really are
cultivating the Ziwei Method.

03:15.340 --> 03:16.500
If you insist,

03:17.540 --> 03:18.540
I'll never let you

03:18.540 --> 03:19.540
get the Jade Sunflower.

03:20.170 --> 03:21.010
Zhao.

03:28.500 --> 03:29.340
Where is she?

03:30.260 --> 03:31.100
Search!

03:41.660 --> 03:43.010
Zhao, look.

03:43.010 --> 03:45.220
The persimmon cakes
we sent to Luoying Valley years ago

03:45.220 --> 03:46.690
were picked from this tree.

03:49.170 --> 03:50.690
So you really are Shi Tieqiao.

03:50.690 --> 03:52.220
(Shi brothers, Shi Tieqiao)
Uncle Tieqiao.

03:52.220 --> 03:53.570
I never dreamed

03:54.260 --> 03:55.100
I'd see Zhao

03:55.260 --> 03:56.130
in my lifetime.

03:57.100 --> 03:58.290
You look more like your mother,

03:58.980 --> 03:59.820
but your eyes

04:00.660 --> 04:01.610
take after your aunt.

04:03.950 --> 04:05.570
This place is so similar to
Luoying Valley.

04:06.410 --> 04:08.170
What a wonderful retreat.

04:08.780 --> 04:10.220
No wonder we couldn't find it.

04:12.010 --> 04:13.100
It's surrounded by mountains.

04:13.500 --> 04:14.380
Warm air creates mist.

04:15.010 --> 04:15.850
Mountains hidden in fog.

04:16.140 --> 04:17.580
Truly hard to track.

04:19.730 --> 04:20.570
Just put it there.

04:22.100 --> 04:23.250
Others can retreat

04:23.250 --> 04:25.410
with their small families,

04:25.410 --> 04:28.100
but ours has always been a big clan.

04:28.100 --> 04:31.170
All those aunts and uncles.

04:31.170 --> 04:33.140
Including your second uncle
and fourth great-uncle.

04:33.140 --> 04:34.810
Over a hundred people total.

04:34.810 --> 04:37.540
If your aunt hadn't found this place,

04:37.540 --> 04:38.930
we could never have retreated

04:38.930 --> 04:39.980
even if we wanted to.

04:41.700 --> 04:42.660
You two youngsters

04:43.370 --> 04:44.980
went to such trouble to lure me out.

04:45.410 --> 04:46.660
What's this all about?

04:55.610 --> 04:56.610
Thank you, Uncle Tieqiao.

04:59.140 --> 05:00.730
Lu Chengnan's tomb

05:00.730 --> 05:02.340
was indeed built by us brothers.

05:03.370 --> 05:05.900
But that pillar

05:05.900 --> 05:08.020
must have been added later by Haosheng.

05:08.020 --> 05:09.900
Haosheng admired Lu Chengnan's character

05:09.900 --> 05:11.900
but couldn't erect a monument openly.

05:12.980 --> 05:13.820
So

05:14.050 --> 05:15.290
he built this pillar,

05:17.410 --> 05:18.980
but it ruined our design.

05:20.850 --> 05:21.980
Uncle Chang meant well.

05:23.080 --> 05:23.930
Well, he...

05:23.930 --> 05:25.580
Died because of that act of kindness.

05:26.410 --> 05:27.410
Uncle Tieqiao, do you know

05:29.250 --> 05:31.490
about the massacre
of Uncle Chang's clan?

05:31.780 --> 05:32.930
Of course I do.

05:32.930 --> 05:33.930
As his brother,

05:35.580 --> 05:36.900
why did you do nothing?

05:42.540 --> 05:43.930
Back when we left.

05:44.660 --> 05:46.490
Pingshu repeatedly told us

05:47.340 --> 05:48.180
to leave

05:48.490 --> 05:49.810
completely.

05:50.100 --> 05:51.050
Step away from Jianghu

05:51.730 --> 05:53.250
means no half-measures.

05:53.730 --> 05:56.100
No matter
if Jianghu sees endless battles

05:56.850 --> 05:58.290
or a bloodbath,

05:58.660 --> 06:01.610
it has nothing to do with you.

06:02.660 --> 06:03.500
In fact, back then,

06:03.900 --> 06:06.490
your aunt also advised Haosheng.

06:07.980 --> 06:09.170
Either recruit followers

06:09.490 --> 06:11.020
to avoid being easily destroyed,

06:11.410 --> 06:12.250
or

06:12.980 --> 06:14.170
like me,

06:14.580 --> 06:16.540
retreat to the mountains resolutely.

06:17.140 --> 06:18.020
The worst

06:18.490 --> 06:19.900
is being half-retired

06:20.900 --> 06:21.810
like Haosheng.

06:22.660 --> 06:23.660
Ms. Cai

06:24.020 --> 06:24.930
truly has insight.

06:25.580 --> 06:26.660
Over the past ten years,

06:27.580 --> 06:29.850
the brave elders of the Chang clan

06:29.850 --> 06:31.050
have either aged, fallen ill,

06:32.140 --> 06:33.220
or passed away.

06:33.810 --> 06:35.660
Chang Fort lost its ability
to defend itself long ago.

06:36.290 --> 06:38.900
But Uncle Chang still
went down the mountain often

06:39.540 --> 06:41.340
to get involved in Jianghu affairs.

06:46.490 --> 06:48.170
He couldn't let us go.

06:49.610 --> 06:50.580
Staying or leaving

06:51.540 --> 06:52.930
was our choice.

06:53.220 --> 06:54.250
It has nothing to do with you.

06:55.020 --> 06:55.860
No need to feel guilty.

06:56.900 --> 06:57.740
However,

06:57.930 --> 06:59.100
Chang clan's mechanism

06:59.490 --> 07:01.140
changes its formation core
every three years.

07:02.900 --> 07:04.810
Without a familiar guide,

07:05.290 --> 07:07.100
outsiders can't enter.

07:08.020 --> 07:09.220
Who would have thought...

07:09.980 --> 07:10.820
Uncle Tieqiao,

07:11.780 --> 07:13.980
where is the Jade Sunflower

07:13.980 --> 07:14.820
Lu Chengnan took out?

07:16.850 --> 07:17.930
Jade Sunflower?

07:20.070 --> 07:20.930
What's wrong with you?

07:20.930 --> 07:21.770
Mu.

07:56.290 --> 07:57.130
You're awake.

08:06.580 --> 08:08.050
Your pulse is finally back to normal.

08:09.020 --> 08:09.860
You know,

08:10.120 --> 08:11.660
when I was little,
I was also in poor health,

08:12.040 --> 08:12.980
often had high fevers.

08:13.660 --> 08:14.780
But I'd cry and fuss,

08:15.050 --> 08:16.220
and talk nonsense.

08:16.540 --> 08:18.250
Wanted the whole Luoying Valley to know.

08:18.250 --> 08:19.540
That way, Uncle Douhua and others would

08:19.540 --> 08:21.220
bring me lots of snacks and drinks.

08:22.140 --> 08:23.250
Not like you.

08:24.050 --> 08:26.410
Burning up all night without a sound.

08:26.410 --> 08:27.490
You're quite tough.

08:28.410 --> 08:30.540
I got used to this before I was five.

08:30.810 --> 08:32.890
Crying or fussing,

08:33.130 --> 08:34.490
someone has to care.

08:35.650 --> 08:36.820
If no one cares,

08:37.610 --> 08:38.820
what's the point?

08:39.850 --> 08:40.690
Besides,

08:41.100 --> 08:42.490
we all die eventually.

08:45.130 --> 08:46.490
When did the poison strike?

08:46.990 --> 08:47.830
Why didn't you tell me

08:47.840 --> 08:49.100
something so important?

08:49.100 --> 08:51.010
Would it make any difference?

08:51.730 --> 08:53.850
I shouldn't even exist.

08:55.980 --> 08:56.820
Except for my father.

08:58.340 --> 08:59.940
Everyone wishes me gone.

09:06.580 --> 09:07.490
Don't worry.

09:08.980 --> 09:11.130
I have my father's Innate Circulation,

09:11.130 --> 09:13.100
plus the medicine
you went through so much trouble

09:13.100 --> 09:15.220
to bring me from the Hanhai Mountains.

09:15.220 --> 09:16.530
I won't die anytime soon.

09:17.850 --> 09:19.130
Won't die.

09:19.580 --> 09:20.940
Do you know your pulse almost stopped

09:20.940 --> 09:22.300
when the poison struck last night?

09:29.130 --> 09:29.970
Zhao,

09:31.850 --> 09:32.940
I made you worry again.

09:34.180 --> 09:35.020
I'm sorry.

09:35.730 --> 09:36.700
But truly, I'm fine,

09:37.300 --> 09:38.650
I haven't found the Man in Black,

09:39.820 --> 09:40.890
haven't avenged the Chang clan,

09:41.420 --> 09:42.580
haven't avenged my father.

09:42.580 --> 09:43.420
Avenge, avenge.

09:43.770 --> 09:44.730
If the poison strikes,

09:44.730 --> 09:45.810
- you'll do nothing.
- If that day comes,

09:47.010 --> 09:47.850
forget me,

09:49.180 --> 09:50.700
and continue as Miss Cai,

09:52.580 --> 09:53.580
Manager Cai.

09:59.060 --> 09:59.900
Don't speak nonsense.

10:02.730 --> 10:05.220
This is Uncle Tieqiao's
secret detox soup.

10:05.220 --> 10:06.700
It can even suppress corpse poison.

10:06.700 --> 10:07.850
Drink it. You won't die from it.

10:15.130 --> 10:16.180
Alright.

10:31.820 --> 10:32.770
What's the matter?

10:32.770 --> 10:33.850
Not feeling well again?

10:35.980 --> 10:36.820
It's so bitter.

10:37.250 --> 10:38.490
I crave some Smileys.

10:50.580 --> 10:52.060
I didn't make you get poisoned.

10:52.340 --> 10:53.820
Why should I make you food?

11:02.100 --> 11:02.940
Uncle Tiefeng?

11:03.100 --> 11:05.460
(Shi brothers, Shi Tiefeng)

11:05.490 --> 11:06.330
Zhao!

11:09.980 --> 11:11.420
What delicious food are you making?

11:11.420 --> 11:12.260
It smells amazing.

11:14.010 --> 11:14.850
Smiley.

11:16.250 --> 11:17.890
Pingshu made it once years ago.

11:17.890 --> 11:19.820
Haosheng and the others ate it all.

11:19.820 --> 11:21.580
I didn't get any!

11:21.580 --> 11:22.730
Quick, give me some.

11:27.730 --> 11:28.700
Uncle Tiefeng, help yourself.

11:28.700 --> 11:29.850
Just leave one piece for my friend.

11:30.420 --> 11:31.260
Friend?

11:32.220 --> 11:33.770
You mean that Mu, right?

11:34.370 --> 11:35.530
I heard from Tieqiao.

11:35.530 --> 11:37.610
He said Mu is quite good-looking.

11:38.250 --> 11:39.250
Is he your sweetheart?

11:43.420 --> 11:44.340
How could that be?

11:44.820 --> 11:46.420
What's there to be shy about?

11:46.730 --> 11:48.060
You're talented and he's handsome.

11:48.220 --> 11:49.490
You're a perfect match.

11:49.490 --> 11:51.220
Though he's from the demon sect,

11:51.220 --> 11:52.980
not all demon sect members are bad.

11:52.980 --> 11:54.770
The one who helped us
get the Jade Sunflower

11:54.770 --> 11:55.770
to heal

11:55.770 --> 11:56.700
was also the demon sect...

11:59.890 --> 12:02.010
Do you mean aunt's friend,

12:02.420 --> 12:03.490
the masked one?

12:04.700 --> 12:06.300
So tasty, truly delicious.

12:06.650 --> 12:07.490
I just remembered

12:07.490 --> 12:08.370
I have something to do.

12:12.420 --> 12:13.260
Uncle Tiefeng!

12:16.780 --> 12:20.020
(Kind and Hospitable)

12:23.850 --> 12:24.690
Zhizhen.

12:25.370 --> 12:27.820
Look, what has your son done?

12:27.820 --> 12:29.420
Luckily Pingchun hasn't arrived.

12:29.420 --> 12:30.490
If he had come,

12:30.490 --> 12:31.820
he'd definitely fight you.

12:34.580 --> 12:35.980
I failed to teach my son well.

12:36.830 --> 12:38.020
I'm sorry about Pingchun,

12:38.450 --> 12:39.490
and Zhao.

12:40.010 --> 12:41.520
When I get back to Peiqiong Manor,

12:41.990 --> 12:43.250
I'll break that boy's legs.

12:43.250 --> 12:45.180
What good will breaking his legs do?

12:45.180 --> 12:46.490
Do you want Zhao

12:47.250 --> 12:48.130
to marry a cripple?

12:49.700 --> 12:50.610
Don't worry.

12:51.300 --> 12:53.820
I have a way to fix this.

12:54.300 --> 12:56.100
Your son refuses the marriage,
doesn't he?

12:56.580 --> 12:57.650
My son does.

12:58.300 --> 13:00.940
I think Yuzhi and Zhao
are a great match.

13:02.610 --> 13:03.700
Song Shijun.

13:03.700 --> 13:04.820
Had this in mind all along?

13:05.820 --> 13:07.700
I wondered why you're so eager.

13:07.700 --> 13:09.610
What does Yuqi and Zhao's marriage

13:09.610 --> 13:10.770
have to do with the Guangtian Sect?

13:11.010 --> 13:12.420
- Yet you ran faster than me.
- This...

13:12.420 --> 13:13.490
What are you talking about?

13:13.490 --> 13:14.890
The Six Sects are united.

13:14.890 --> 13:16.530
How can it be unrelated to
the Guangtian Sect?

13:16.530 --> 13:18.100
I care about the younger generation.

13:18.100 --> 13:19.490
Enough. I'm not arguing with you.

13:19.980 --> 13:21.060
I just want to remind you

13:21.940 --> 13:24.220
Yuzhi and Lingbo are already engaged.

13:24.220 --> 13:25.060
Father.

13:27.300 --> 13:28.140
Father.

13:29.610 --> 13:30.450
Father.

13:30.620 --> 13:32.250
I want to withdraw my engagement
to Song Yuzhi.

13:36.660 --> 13:37.520
Lingbo.

13:37.520 --> 13:39.180
Are you serious?

13:42.720 --> 13:43.730
Father, please grant my wish.

13:49.230 --> 13:50.090
Grant it.

13:50.100 --> 13:51.100
Definitely.

13:52.820 --> 13:53.770
Lingbo.

13:53.770 --> 13:55.220
You've finally come to your senses.

13:55.220 --> 13:56.610
That rascal Yuzhi

13:56.610 --> 13:58.010
is not worthy of you.

13:59.220 --> 14:00.610
I also think he's not worthy.

14:01.100 --> 14:02.850
I was blinded by the engagement before,

14:02.850 --> 14:04.180
but now I see clearly.

14:04.180 --> 14:05.020
He's

14:05.420 --> 14:06.980
cold and unfeeling,

14:07.490 --> 14:08.490
stubborn and dull,

14:09.250 --> 14:10.300
narrow-minded,

14:11.030 --> 14:12.100
and lacks any sense of romance.

14:13.490 --> 14:14.530
He's truly not worthy of me.

14:15.490 --> 14:16.520
My future husband

14:17.340 --> 14:18.490
should cherish,

14:19.010 --> 14:19.850
understand,

14:20.060 --> 14:20.900
and protect me.

14:21.220 --> 14:23.130
Even a relationship
like Zhou Yuqi and Min Xinrou's,

14:23.940 --> 14:25.060
for all its shamelessness,

14:26.940 --> 14:28.530
is better than a forced marriage.

14:31.580 --> 14:32.420
Father.

14:32.700 --> 14:33.540
Uncle.

14:33.700 --> 14:34.650
I've made it clear to him.

14:35.220 --> 14:36.220
From now on,

14:38.530 --> 14:39.700
we're just fellow disciples.

14:46.300 --> 14:47.420
As long as it's clear, it's fine.

14:48.250 --> 14:49.420
Clarifying it is enough.

14:49.820 --> 14:50.660
Yunke.

14:51.180 --> 14:52.420
Why not take this chance

14:52.770 --> 14:54.250
to change their engagements?

14:57.060 --> 14:58.490
Nie Zhe is on the run.

14:59.300 --> 15:00.490
Zhao is missing.

15:01.490 --> 15:02.980
I truly have no mind for this.

15:04.700 --> 15:05.770
Let's go to Taichu Temple first.

15:24.700 --> 15:25.580
Dalou, you're here.

15:26.370 --> 15:27.210
Lady Yin.

15:27.420 --> 15:28.530
I made you ginger soup.

15:29.100 --> 15:30.220
The weather is getting cold,

15:30.420 --> 15:31.420
be careful of the cold.

15:40.530 --> 15:42.010
Your master
went down the mountain again?

15:43.300 --> 15:44.730
Master went to handle Zhao's matter.

15:49.940 --> 15:52.340
How long have you been on the mountain?

15:53.730 --> 15:54.570
Twenty years.

15:56.490 --> 15:57.700
Twenty years.

15:59.100 --> 16:01.610
Lingbo wasn't even born then.

16:03.650 --> 16:05.180
Lingbo is braver than me.

16:07.370 --> 16:09.300
If I had her courage back then,

16:10.490 --> 16:11.650
I wouldn't be like this now.

16:16.130 --> 16:16.970
Lady Yin.

16:17.490 --> 16:18.850
Master has always kept you in his heart.

16:19.580 --> 16:20.730
But he's stuck with trivial matters

16:21.610 --> 16:22.730
and has to mediate.

16:25.250 --> 16:26.220
Maybe.

17:02.820 --> 17:03.980
Gentle wind, light rain.

17:04.860 --> 17:05.980
Smoke from cottages.

17:06.570 --> 17:08.290
Spending the rest of my life here

17:08.980 --> 17:09.820
wouldn't be bad.

17:10.230 --> 17:11.490
You're not going to catch the culprit?

17:12.010 --> 17:12.850
Zhao.

17:14.090 --> 17:15.900
Do you really want me to keep digging?

17:17.900 --> 17:18.860
What do you mean?

17:21.220 --> 17:22.700
The sword formation used by

17:23.180 --> 17:24.330
the Man in Black who ambushed us.

17:25.140 --> 17:26.770
Doesn't it feel familiar to you?

17:33.490 --> 17:34.570
Not the Xuantian Sword Formation.

17:35.250 --> 17:36.770
Just somewhat similar.

17:36.770 --> 17:38.700
Both originate from
the Big Dipper's footwork,

17:39.570 --> 17:41.700
but are fundamentally different.

17:41.700 --> 17:42.770
The leader's

17:43.860 --> 17:44.700
sword techniques.

17:48.380 --> 17:49.730
Definitely not from Qingque Sect.

17:51.380 --> 17:52.220
Dinner's ready,

17:54.230 --> 17:55.110
Uncle Tieqiao.

17:55.110 --> 17:56.380
Time to eat.

17:56.380 --> 17:57.250
You've worked hard.

17:57.270 --> 17:58.140
This is your favorite.

18:01.490 --> 18:03.380
These days the dishes are mostly light.

18:03.770 --> 18:05.490
Why so much meat and fish today?

18:05.980 --> 18:08.860
Well, Mu's injury is almost healed.

18:08.860 --> 18:11.900
Consider this your farewell dinner.

18:15.730 --> 18:16.570
Come on.

18:17.380 --> 18:18.250
Eat more meat.

18:20.180 --> 18:21.530
Uncle Tieqiao, you have some too.

18:23.290 --> 18:25.700
I know why you came here.

18:26.620 --> 18:27.530
Once it's said,

18:27.770 --> 18:28.770
it's time for you to leave.

18:29.700 --> 18:30.940
Lu Chengnan was seriously injured

18:32.330 --> 18:33.170
and

18:34.050 --> 18:35.380
fled to Chang Fort

18:35.900 --> 18:37.010
with Mu Zhengming's help.

18:37.380 --> 18:38.810
Before my father was wounded,

18:39.290 --> 18:40.730
he did rescue many in secret.

18:41.220 --> 18:42.700
Mr. Mu is a good man.

18:43.490 --> 18:44.330
Unfortunately,

18:45.140 --> 18:47.420
Haosheng immediately
sent a carrier pigeon to Pingshu.

18:47.420 --> 18:49.530
We brothers were with her,

18:49.860 --> 18:51.140
so we rushed to Chang clan at once.

18:51.980 --> 18:52.820
By then,

18:53.040 --> 18:54.530
Lu Chengnan's heart meridians
were shattered.

18:55.140 --> 18:56.090
On his deathbed.

18:56.090 --> 18:57.740
(Li Sect, Lu Chengnan)

18:58.250 --> 18:59.860
Why give the Jade Sunflower to me?

19:00.700 --> 19:01.770
My master's skills

19:02.490 --> 19:03.570
reached perfection

19:04.050 --> 19:05.420
years ago.

19:06.330 --> 19:07.290
At his age,

19:08.090 --> 19:09.490
he shouldn't have improved much.

19:10.380 --> 19:11.420
But this year,

19:13.180 --> 19:16.660
I noticed his power surged dramatically.

19:17.250 --> 19:18.530
Secretly, master

19:18.530 --> 19:19.700
ordered Nie clan's disciples

19:20.250 --> 19:22.420
to massacre
many upright martial artists.

19:22.860 --> 19:24.380
They even captured many people alive.

19:25.380 --> 19:26.660
Soon after, what were thrown out

19:27.810 --> 19:29.090
were bodies upon bodies,

19:29.980 --> 19:31.250
dried and lifeless.

19:32.050 --> 19:33.770
All had broken meridians,

19:34.530 --> 19:35.730
destroyed dantians.

19:36.250 --> 19:38.050
All the essence and vital energy
in their body

19:38.490 --> 19:40.090
were completely drained away.

19:40.770 --> 19:41.730
Only then did I realize

19:42.940 --> 19:44.810
my master
had been cultivating our sect's

19:45.660 --> 19:48.730
lost supreme skill,

19:49.220 --> 19:50.380
Ziwei Method.

19:51.050 --> 19:52.860
It requires the Jade Sunflower

19:52.860 --> 19:55.570
to absorb others'
danyuan and inner power.

19:55.940 --> 19:57.140
No wonder many top martial artists

19:57.140 --> 19:59.900
have disappeared
without a trace in recent years.

20:00.770 --> 20:01.860
But gradually,

20:02.730 --> 20:05.770
my master's mind became abnormal.

20:06.700 --> 20:07.900
Sometimes insane.

20:09.570 --> 20:13.730
He even targeted our sect's top experts.

20:14.050 --> 20:15.220
If this continues,

20:16.010 --> 20:18.490
not only will our sect brothers
be slaughtered,

20:19.140 --> 20:22.530
master will also
go mad from cultivation.

20:22.810 --> 20:24.660
So you stole the Jade Sunflower

20:24.660 --> 20:26.530
to stop your master,

20:26.530 --> 20:27.700
make him turn back.

20:28.250 --> 20:29.490
Even though I and Ms. Cai

20:29.980 --> 20:31.490
have never met,

20:31.490 --> 20:33.330
I've long admired you.

20:34.420 --> 20:35.810
You act boldly

20:36.180 --> 20:37.250
and with integrity.

20:37.660 --> 20:39.010
Far better than those

20:39.700 --> 20:41.380
rigid,

20:41.380 --> 20:43.140
selfish old folks.

20:44.010 --> 20:44.860
The future

20:45.330 --> 20:46.730
of the world

20:47.700 --> 20:48.770
is in your hands

20:49.900 --> 20:51.050
to decide.

20:59.980 --> 21:01.180
True friendship

21:02.090 --> 21:03.180
is worth trusting with life.

21:04.490 --> 21:06.490
Aunt and Lu Chengnan are both heroes.

21:07.090 --> 21:07.930
Sadly,

21:09.530 --> 21:10.810
heroes never live long.

21:11.530 --> 21:12.730
Better to be like me.

21:13.090 --> 21:13.980
Care about nothing

21:14.330 --> 21:15.530
and live freely.

21:16.810 --> 21:17.940
So

21:18.730 --> 21:19.810
the Jade Sunflower

21:20.290 --> 21:21.900
is still with Ms. Cai's.

21:21.900 --> 21:23.290
But my parents said

21:24.180 --> 21:26.090
there's no trace of it
in Luoying Valley.

21:26.810 --> 21:28.090
Pingshu once said

21:28.530 --> 21:31.420
this thing is a curse.

21:32.140 --> 21:33.700
You're both so young,

21:34.940 --> 21:35.810
if you can't find it,

21:36.730 --> 21:38.770
better give up.

21:39.140 --> 21:40.090
Don't let this

21:41.140 --> 21:42.010
cause more trouble.

21:45.980 --> 21:46.820
Fine,

21:47.290 --> 21:49.660
maybe it's all aunt's will from heaven.

21:50.090 --> 21:50.930
Senior,

21:51.570 --> 21:52.770
what exactly does

21:53.220 --> 21:54.330
the Jade Sunflower look like?

21:54.770 --> 21:56.530
It was burned

21:57.730 --> 21:58.770
in the Li Sect treasury.

21:59.010 --> 22:00.180
Only left with…

22:11.220 --> 22:12.250
Since it's a curse,

22:14.140 --> 22:14.980
why cling to it?

22:16.860 --> 22:17.700
Tieqiao.

22:18.860 --> 22:20.050
Hurry, come see Zigui with me.

22:20.900 --> 22:22.050
Zigui has awakened?

22:22.050 --> 22:23.140
It must be time.

22:24.420 --> 22:25.730
The Shi twins

22:25.730 --> 22:26.770
have Zigui?

22:26.770 --> 22:27.860
Zigui

22:27.860 --> 22:28.770
has been comatose for years.

22:29.380 --> 22:30.290
Now he's awake.

22:31.220 --> 22:32.330
It must be fate.

22:32.770 --> 22:33.660
You two.

22:33.660 --> 22:34.530
Come with me.

22:35.380 --> 22:36.220
Let's go.

23:00.490 --> 23:01.620
Pingshu.

23:04.660 --> 23:05.660
She is not Pingshu.

23:06.140 --> 23:07.940
She's the daughter
of Xiaofeng and Pingchun.

23:07.940 --> 23:08.780
Cai Zhao.

23:14.090 --> 23:14.940
Cai Zhao.

23:15.690 --> 23:16.530
Yes.

23:16.530 --> 23:19.220
She's also a disciple of Yunke.

23:19.700 --> 23:20.980
Xiaofeng and

23:20.980 --> 23:23.250
Pingchun's daughter.

23:23.660 --> 23:25.530
She's grown up so much.

23:26.180 --> 23:27.380
Back then, we promised

23:27.940 --> 23:29.730
to carry Xiaofeng

23:29.730 --> 23:30.620
at her wedding.

23:31.420 --> 23:33.330
But I broke my word.

23:34.420 --> 23:35.290
Zhao.

23:35.730 --> 23:36.570
How's

23:37.220 --> 23:38.770
your mother?

23:40.900 --> 23:41.980
My mother is fine.

23:42.490 --> 23:43.530
And you are...

23:43.810 --> 23:45.810
You must be Yin Dai's seventh disciple.

23:46.420 --> 23:47.260
Guo Zigui.

23:48.980 --> 23:50.860
Who is Uncle Guo?

23:50.860 --> 23:53.700
He's the uncle
who grew up with your mother.

23:53.700 --> 23:55.620
And also my and your Uncle Qi's
junior brother.

23:56.620 --> 23:57.770
How could that be?

23:58.660 --> 23:59.730
Uncle Guo

24:00.180 --> 24:01.620
is the same age as my mother.

24:02.490 --> 24:03.700
Your Uncle Guo

24:03.700 --> 24:05.810
was born into
a wealthy family in Jiangdong.

24:05.810 --> 24:08.490
A charmer by the bridge at dusk.

24:09.140 --> 24:11.250
He idled all day.

24:11.900 --> 24:13.420
A laughing

24:13.420 --> 24:14.420
and cheerful lad.

24:15.530 --> 24:18.900
Your maternal grandparents'home was
just one alley away from the Guo clan's.

24:18.900 --> 24:20.730
Whenever your mother met Zigui,

24:20.730 --> 24:23.770
it was bound to
stir trouble and headaches for all.

24:23.770 --> 24:25.420
We were childhood sweethearts,

24:25.420 --> 24:26.720
as close as siblings.

24:26.730 --> 24:27.990
As close as siblings.

24:32.220 --> 24:33.180
Uncle Guo.

24:33.790 --> 24:35.180
(Qingque Sect, Guo Zigui)
Mom has been looking for you.

24:35.810 --> 24:37.140
Why haven't you come back?

24:37.700 --> 24:38.540
Xiaofeng

24:39.010 --> 24:41.420
must want me to join in her games.

24:42.490 --> 24:43.330
Kid.

24:44.050 --> 24:46.010
How is your aunt?

24:47.220 --> 24:48.380
My aunt, she...

24:56.490 --> 24:58.050
She's at Luoying Valley.

24:58.660 --> 24:59.700
She's in poor health,

25:00.490 --> 25:02.180
resting there to recover.

25:03.180 --> 25:04.380
Resting is good.

25:04.900 --> 25:06.090
Your aunt…

25:07.140 --> 25:09.420
has suffered too much.

25:11.660 --> 25:12.500
Zhao.

25:12.940 --> 25:14.420
Tell me.

25:15.090 --> 25:16.490
How are things in the sect?

25:17.180 --> 25:18.530
Come, help me up.

25:19.090 --> 25:19.930
Alright.

25:22.770 --> 25:23.610
Sit down.

25:25.860 --> 25:26.980
Qingque Sect.

25:29.180 --> 25:30.490
How is it now?

25:30.490 --> 25:31.570
Everything's good

25:32.620 --> 25:33.770
except the cook isn't great.

25:34.450 --> 25:35.330
You know

25:35.330 --> 25:36.220
my master's personality.

25:36.660 --> 25:37.770
Lenient with himself.

25:37.770 --> 25:39.180
Even more so with others.

25:39.180 --> 25:41.250
So now at Qingque Sect,

25:41.250 --> 25:42.250
everyone

25:42.250 --> 25:44.620
loves gathering
to chat.

25:44.620 --> 25:46.380
The sunflower seed shells
they crack each day

25:46.380 --> 25:48.220
can pile up into a big basket.

25:49.010 --> 25:50.730
Luckily Uncle Li Wenxun is there,

25:50.730 --> 25:52.180
so the sect rules still hold firm.

25:55.420 --> 25:56.700
Not like

25:58.380 --> 25:59.380
back in our day.

26:00.010 --> 26:00.900
But

26:01.660 --> 26:03.290
so many senior brothers

26:03.700 --> 26:04.900
are gone.

26:05.730 --> 26:07.050
Uncle Lei is still around.

26:07.050 --> 26:09.090
He loves rambling about pill quality

26:09.290 --> 26:10.730
in the Herb Hut.

26:11.530 --> 26:12.540
He's someone

26:15.090 --> 26:16.220
who loves looking good.

26:18.010 --> 26:19.900
Once he's dressed up,

26:21.010 --> 26:23.180
he likes going where it's crowded.

26:25.140 --> 26:28.010
Now he stays in the Herb Hut all day.

26:28.420 --> 26:30.380
He must be wounded.

26:31.660 --> 26:34.810
Just a few small scars on his face.

26:36.010 --> 26:37.010
I don't think it's a big deal.

26:37.490 --> 26:38.940
I think it makes him look more valiant.

26:39.380 --> 26:40.940
If it's only a few small scars,

26:42.490 --> 26:44.220
he could heal them himself.

26:45.570 --> 26:47.570
There must be other injuries.

26:48.660 --> 26:50.900
Luckily, he's still alive.

26:51.490 --> 26:53.430
Being alive is enough.

26:56.530 --> 26:57.370
Uncle Guo.

26:57.770 --> 26:58.610
Let me do it.

26:59.290 --> 27:00.130
Let me handle it.

27:02.220 --> 27:03.060
Uncle Guo.

27:07.860 --> 27:10.220
This is clearly
draining Uncle Guo's vitality.

27:10.220 --> 27:11.620
This is trading the future for now.

27:11.620 --> 27:12.460
Zhao.

27:14.050 --> 27:15.490
Zigui's injuries are far too severe.

27:15.490 --> 27:17.250
This is the only way left
to keep him alive.

27:40.220 --> 27:41.180
Zhao.

27:42.490 --> 27:44.900
Bring some things back for me.

27:48.090 --> 27:50.010
Guo clan of Jiangdong

27:50.010 --> 27:51.860
is gone now.

27:51.860 --> 27:52.940
These are my

27:55.380 --> 27:57.980
only remaining belongings.

27:58.900 --> 28:00.330
Consider it

28:02.380 --> 28:04.010
as extra dowry
for your mom.

28:08.490 --> 28:10.010
- And your aunt...
- Zigui.

28:14.250 --> 28:15.180
Pingshu.

28:20.140 --> 28:20.980
Zigui.

28:21.250 --> 28:22.090
I promise.

28:22.220 --> 28:23.060
Next time.

28:23.220 --> 28:24.810
Next time I'll take you to roam Jianghu.

28:25.020 --> 28:25.900
Zigui.

28:25.900 --> 28:27.570
Wait until you've mastered your skills.

28:27.860 --> 28:29.420
We're out to uphold justice.

28:29.420 --> 28:30.570
Not just out for leisure.

28:31.180 --> 28:32.900
With your current clumsy moves,

28:32.900 --> 28:33.770
blood will make you faint.

28:34.180 --> 28:35.140
When the time comes,

28:35.140 --> 28:36.250
we'd have to carry you back.

28:39.700 --> 28:40.540
Zigui.

28:40.810 --> 28:41.650
Master already said,

28:41.980 --> 28:42.820
you've got talent.

28:43.180 --> 28:44.020
You'll master it for sure.

28:47.620 --> 28:50.290
Come on.

28:50.290 --> 28:51.570
- Drink up. Drink up.
- Drink up.

28:51.570 --> 28:52.490
Cheers.

28:52.490 --> 28:53.330
Come on.

28:54.090 --> 28:54.930
Fill it up, fill it up.

28:55.290 --> 28:56.130
Alright.

28:56.980 --> 28:59.220
Zigui, join us for a drink.

28:59.700 --> 29:01.250
Breeze.

29:01.620 --> 29:02.460
- Here!
- Hurry over.

29:03.050 --> 29:04.140
Come on.

29:06.620 --> 29:09.010
- Drink, drink!
- Cheers!

29:12.940 --> 29:15.490
I saw Pingshu raised the Sunshine Blade.

29:16.010 --> 29:16.980
Those bandits were so scared.

29:16.980 --> 29:19.010
And they scrambled away in seconds.

29:19.530 --> 29:21.860
One even fainted on the spot!

29:24.140 --> 29:25.610
Zigui, here.

29:27.090 --> 29:28.010
It hurts, it hurts!

29:28.010 --> 29:28.980
Zigui.

29:28.980 --> 29:31.220
- Scared of pain? Then why learn martial arts?
- Exactly.

29:31.220 --> 29:33.530
Because Lord Yin personally
went to Jiangdong and

29:33.530 --> 29:34.940
insisted on
taking Zigui as his disciple.

29:34.940 --> 29:35.780
Right?

29:36.900 --> 29:38.860
I heard the Mu Wei Palace
was just renovated.

29:38.860 --> 29:39.900
Your family paid for that again.

29:40.660 --> 29:42.090
As disciples of Qingque Sect,

29:42.090 --> 29:44.050
it's only right to serve the sect.

29:49.620 --> 29:53.700
(Lord of Qingque Sect, Yin Dai)

29:53.730 --> 29:55.700
The demon sect has evil ambitions.

29:56.770 --> 29:58.180
Jianghu is in danger.

29:59.940 --> 30:01.490
Disciples of the Six Sects,

30:01.900 --> 30:03.620
you must do your duty

30:04.940 --> 30:06.490
and eliminate the devil!

30:07.010 --> 30:09.660
(Righteous Spirit)
Eliminate the devil!

30:09.660 --> 30:10.570
In that battle,

30:11.050 --> 30:12.860
almost all the younger disciples went

30:13.700 --> 30:16.330
except Qiu Yuanfeng,
who was recovering from injuries.

30:19.140 --> 30:20.490
- What are you doing here?
- Pingshu.

30:20.490 --> 30:22.140
Yuanjing, keep Zigui safe.

30:22.140 --> 30:22.980
Okay.

30:25.090 --> 30:26.140
Fight!

30:27.050 --> 30:28.330
Fight!

30:39.570 --> 30:40.660
Zigui, over here.

30:47.290 --> 30:48.660
Wang Yuanjing took Zigui

30:49.490 --> 30:50.860
and got lost in the EightClaw Prison.

31:12.980 --> 31:14.810
They accidentally
separated in the chaos.

31:38.700 --> 31:39.540
Where's Zigui?

31:40.010 --> 31:41.380
I got separated from Zigui.

31:41.980 --> 31:43.570
- I'll go find him.
- I saw him running back.

31:44.050 --> 31:45.010
He must've gone back.

31:50.570 --> 31:51.980
But never returned.

31:53.330 --> 31:54.570
Pingshu snuck into the Youming Path

31:55.570 --> 31:57.220
several times to find him,

31:58.290 --> 32:00.050
but the Hanhai Mountains are too big.

32:01.530 --> 32:02.660
Impossible to locate.

32:14.010 --> 32:14.850
Never thought

32:15.530 --> 32:16.770
he's so tough.

32:17.700 --> 32:19.570
Every bone in his body was crushed,

32:20.380 --> 32:21.620
yet he endured.

32:25.770 --> 32:26.940
I won't surrender.

32:28.620 --> 32:29.770
I won't surrender.

32:30.490 --> 32:31.330
Keep beating him.

32:43.740 --> 32:44.980
(Parents alive, when can I go home?)

32:44.980 --> 32:45.820
Father.

32:46.860 --> 32:47.700
Mother.

32:50.290 --> 32:51.220
It hurts.

32:52.220 --> 32:53.140
It hurts.

32:54.220 --> 32:55.060
Mother.

32:55.980 --> 32:57.180
Take me home.

32:58.860 --> 32:59.770
Take me...

32:59.770 --> 33:00.860
Take me home.

33:04.700 --> 33:06.290
Just sign the surrender letter,

33:07.250 --> 33:08.900
and your master will take you home.

33:13.420 --> 33:15.420
Keep dreaming.

33:39.620 --> 33:40.460
Zigui.

33:44.700 --> 33:45.540
Zigui.

33:47.620 --> 33:48.490
Pingshu.

33:48.490 --> 33:49.570
My son.

33:49.570 --> 33:50.410
Father!

33:52.050 --> 33:53.050
Zigui.

33:53.050 --> 33:53.890
Mother.

33:55.860 --> 33:56.810
Come.

33:56.810 --> 33:57.700
Come home with me.

33:58.980 --> 33:59.900
Come home.

34:00.290 --> 34:01.130
My son.

34:02.180 --> 34:03.490
Come home with me.

34:03.490 --> 34:04.330
Zigui.

34:04.900 --> 34:05.740
Come home with me.

34:06.490 --> 34:07.380
Come home.

34:17.820 --> 34:18.660
Come home.

34:18.660 --> 34:19.500
(Respectfully, Guo Zigui)

34:21.130 --> 34:22.010
Come home.

34:24.740 --> 34:27.940
The demon sect sent Zigui's
surrender letter to Yin Dai.

34:29.170 --> 34:30.860
But Yin Dai refused to save him

34:32.090 --> 34:33.340
and even issued a kill order.

34:33.780 --> 34:34.940
Lord Yin.

34:35.780 --> 34:38.170
As long as you save Zigui,

34:38.170 --> 34:41.610
I'll give you all my family property.

34:41.610 --> 34:44.490
Please save Zigui.

34:44.490 --> 34:46.940
Such a cowardly man

34:46.940 --> 34:48.340
deserves to die to prove his loyalty!

34:49.130 --> 34:49.980
No.

34:49.980 --> 34:51.980
- Please, Lord Yin!
- Mr. Guo, Mrs. Guo.

34:52.860 --> 34:53.700
Lord Yin.

34:53.900 --> 34:55.860
Zigui is Beichen disciple.
Why not save him?

34:56.090 --> 34:57.380
Any Qingque Sect disciple

34:58.050 --> 35:00.820
who shows weakness
and surrenders to the enemy

35:00.820 --> 35:02.170
deserves death.

35:02.170 --> 35:04.010
I'm being lenient

35:04.420 --> 35:06.010
by not killing him myself.

35:06.010 --> 35:07.050
He never hurt anyone!

35:07.060 --> 35:07.930
In this world,

35:07.930 --> 35:09.570
not everyone is born a hero.

35:09.570 --> 35:13.050
If everyone is cowardly
and surrenders easily,

35:13.490 --> 35:15.490
what's left of loyalty
and righteousness?

35:15.690 --> 35:18.490
How can the Six Sects of Beichen
command respect?

35:18.820 --> 35:19.940
Is it really wrong to fear death?

35:20.490 --> 35:21.340
Wasn't the reason we

35:21.340 --> 35:23.650
learned martial arts
to rid the world of bullying

35:23.650 --> 35:25.210
and unnecessary sacrifice?

35:26.420 --> 35:27.690
Words mean nothing now.

35:28.690 --> 35:29.530
No one from the Six Sects

35:30.170 --> 35:31.340
will save him.

35:31.940 --> 35:32.940
Whoever does

35:33.860 --> 35:35.490
is deemed a traitor.

35:36.690 --> 35:37.530
Later,

35:38.530 --> 35:39.900
Pingshu searched for a long time

35:41.130 --> 35:42.340
and finally found out

35:43.820 --> 35:47.130
Zigui was locked
in the EightClaw Prison.

35:50.980 --> 35:51.820
Zigui.

35:53.820 --> 35:54.690
Don't beat me.

35:54.860 --> 35:55.900
Don't beat me.

35:56.780 --> 35:57.620
It hurts.

35:58.530 --> 36:00.130
No... Don't hit me.

36:00.860 --> 36:01.700
Zigui.

36:02.380 --> 36:03.300
It's me, Pingshu.

36:11.980 --> 36:12.820
Senior Sister.

36:13.380 --> 36:14.220
Pingshu.

36:15.690 --> 36:16.740
I'm taking you home.

36:17.980 --> 36:18.820
Home.

36:20.740 --> 36:22.650
Home.

36:26.900 --> 36:27.940
Home.

36:32.210 --> 36:34.210
- Home...
- Sadly, the two elders of the Guo clan

36:35.740 --> 36:37.780
never got the chance
to see their son again.

36:39.300 --> 36:41.340
Not long after
returning from Qingque Sect,

36:42.650 --> 36:43.940
they both

36:45.980 --> 36:47.210
died of anger.

36:57.170 --> 36:59.090
Let Zigui retire with you.

36:59.590 --> 37:01.050
He never wanted
anything to do with Jianghu.

37:01.820 --> 37:02.660
Staying here.

37:03.050 --> 37:04.210
A few years of peace, at least.

37:04.490 --> 37:05.330
Pingshu.

37:05.490 --> 37:06.490
You retire too.

37:07.090 --> 37:07.930
This world...

37:09.210 --> 37:10.940
isn't what we imagined.

37:10.940 --> 37:12.940
Then let's make it into
what we imagined.

37:12.940 --> 37:14.220
- Pingshu, you...
- Tieqiao.

37:14.780 --> 37:15.980
Someone has to hold on.

37:41.300 --> 37:42.650
Pingshu!

37:43.980 --> 37:44.820
Zigui.

37:47.570 --> 37:49.780
Pingshu!

38:39.740 --> 38:40.580
Let me do it.

38:42.490 --> 38:43.380
Uncle Guo.

39:02.340 --> 39:03.300
Pingshu.

39:04.980 --> 39:05.910
- Father.
- Try this.

39:07.220 --> 39:08.220
- Mother.
- This one is nice.

39:09.300 --> 39:10.610
- Zigui, come drink.
- Have a taste.

39:11.570 --> 39:12.780
Breeze!

39:30.530 --> 39:31.650
Chang.

39:31.650 --> 39:32.530
Come.

39:32.530 --> 39:33.490
Shi.

39:35.010 --> 39:35.850
Wu.

39:36.170 --> 39:37.010
Zigui.

